text.tspan: Prevalence of anxiety disorders, males vs. females, 2019
Share of population suffering from anxiety disorders, in males versus females. Figures attempt to provide a true estimate (going beyond
reported diagnosis) of anxiety disorder prevalence based on medical, epidemiological data, surveys and meta-regression modelling.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
